  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b89\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baf \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0 \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc8 \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0b89\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bc8- \u0b89\u0bb2\u0b95 \u0bb5\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "World Bank will not provide new financing until Sri Lanka develops appropriate economic policy framework",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "The World Bank has announced that it is not ready to provide new financing to Sri Lanka until an adequate economic policy framework is in place.",
        "In a statement, the World Bank said it is deeply concerned about the worsening economic crisis in Sri Lanka and its impact on the people.",
        "The World Bank said it is redeploying resources under its portfolio of loans to cover shortages in medicines, cooking gas, fertilizer, school meals and financing for poor and vulnerable families.",
        "To date, the World Bank has provided 160 million US dollars in this fund to meet the urgent needs.",
        "\"We will continue to monitor these practices and work closely with organizations that implement credible controls and oversight to ensure these practices reach the poorest and most vulnerable,\" the World Bank said."
      ],
